						"description": "Register an IPN (Instant Payment Notification) URL to receive payment status updates.\n\n**Required:**\n- url: Publicly accessible URL to receive notifications\n- ipn_notification_type: HTTP method (GET or POST)\n\n**Response:**\n- ipn_id: Unique identifier for this IPN registration (save this!)\n- url: Registered URL\n- notification_type: 0 (GET) or 1 (POST)\n- ipn_status: 1 (Active) or 0 (Inactive)"
					},
